  "title": "Quantity Surveyor/ Senior QS (Construction) - 5 days workweek!",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Construction industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Quantity Surveyor </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Quantity Surveyor/ Senior QS</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Islandwide</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5 days, Office Hours</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Basic + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide comprehensive support to the commercial team in both pre-contract and post-contract phases of fast-track projects.</li>\n  <li>Assist with tender preparation, including quantity measurement, Bills of Quantities (BOQ), cost summaries, and price comparisons for tender submissions.</li>\n  <li>Assist with the accurate preparation of progress payment claims, variation orders (VO), and final accounts. Support the measurement and certification of subcontractor payments.</li>\n  <li>Support project budgeting, cost control, and cash flow monitoring.</li>\n  <li>Maintain meticulous documentation of all site events, variations, and correspondence to support claims.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with and support project and safety teams on all commercial and site safety initiatives.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all activities comply with company safety policies and relevant workplace health and safety legislation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least Diploma in Quantity Surveying, Construction Management, or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of relevant quantity surveying experience within a main-con environment.</li>\n  <li>Knowledgeable in construction costs, methods, and materials.</li>\n  <li>Able to start immediately or in short notice.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
